data.title: Joseph & Kathleen Andrews - Calabasas, CA Real Estate Agent
data.meta_description: Find real estate agent & Realtor速 Joseph & Kathleen Andrews in Calabasas, CA on realtor.com速, your source for top rated real estate professionals.
data.text:
We believe a successful real estate transaction begins long before a buyer and seller

agree on price and terms. With over 30 years of real estate sales experience, we have

the skill, insight and knowledge to ensure success of the biggest investment you will

probably ever make. Your Home.

A recent Co-owner of two Real Estate Brokerages, Joe has trained hundreds of

successful Realtors and is recognized for his wealth of knowledge and expertise. As a

community leader, Joe is President Emeritus of the Canoga Park / West Hills Chamber

of Commerce, former Board of Directors Member Canoga Park Neighborhood Council,

West Valley LAPD Boosters, LAPD Topanga Boosters, and the LAPD Jeopardy Youth

at Risk Program. Most recently, Joe has served the Board Chairman for the Valley

Cultural Foundation.

Joe is also the founder and President of the Walk of Hearts速 Foundation, a teacher

recognition program establishing a walk of fame for local teachers nominated by their

students, parents, and peers. Nationally recognized, The Walk of Hearts速

Foundation has honored over 75 exceptional educators and has provided thousands of

dollars in student scholarships.

A native Californian, Katie grew up in the San Fernando Valley and brings over 25 years

in management and leadership experience in Communications and Financial

Services focused on Client Services and Technology Operations. Katie is a long term

member of the Rotary Club of Woodland Hills, former Board of Directors Member

Leukemia & Lymphoma Society, YMCA, and Haven Hills. Katie also serves as the

Executive Director of the Walk of Hearts Foundation.

Joe and Katie's partnership blends 30 years of Real Estate sales experience, with both

business operations and technology experience, allowing our clients to focus on their

careers, and busy lives, while we manage the real estate transaction to a successful

outcome.

If you are interested in buying or selling a property we would love an opportunity to talk about it and share our approach. As local community leaders, and real estate professionals, it would be our honor to work for you.
